subject: Basketball
Suspensions, Dismissals and Resignations
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Debbie Ryan, who built Virginia’s women’s basketball program into a perennial N.C.A.A. tournament team and overcame pancreatic cancer, has resigned after 34 years and 736 victories.
